{"tid":465044,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 鹵水雞脾","createTime":"2017-11-11T06:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T14:05:43.000Z","uid":74981,"like":41,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd873fb9bb3ab0a2e69afa89f342bcbd1bc80e3","tid":465044,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/5u3soh5odb/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F5u3soh5odb%2Fimage.jpg&h=2f16f72e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/1i4zgxmsan/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F1i4zgxmsan%2Fimage.jpg&h=2176f22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>影片如下:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/50LhbdOzAFU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F50LhbdOzAFU&d=CeERpCKrFVwiV386tkw2u57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ff678f60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/50LhbdOzAFU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>材料:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n雞脾1隻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>鹵水汁:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n八角3粒<br />\n<br />\n丁香8粒<br />\n<br />\n桂皮1小片 (可有可無, 我自己無加)<br />\n<br />\n生抽2.5湯匙多少少<br />\n<br />\n老抽1湯匙<br />\n<br />\n酒1湯匙 (有玫瑰露就最好, 冇就用花雕或米酒)<br />\n<br />\n冰糖一小舊, 冇就用片糖一小塊或黃糖1.5至2茶匙代替<br />\n<br />\n水6湯匙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>做法慨述:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 獲落少油燒至微熱爆下D八角同丁香, 然後將其餘鹵水料落獲煮滾.<br />\n<br />\n2. 落雞脾先煮有皮果邊, 滾起收細火浸煮15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n3. 其間如發現煮到D少水得濟可逐次加少少水煮, 如加多左水就開大番少少火煮滾再馬上收細火.<br />\n<br />\n4. 15分鍾後反轉雞脾另一面繼續煮多10分鐘. (其間如發現煮到D少水得濟可逐次加少少水煮, 如加多左水就開大番少少火煮滾再馬上收細火.)<br />\n<br />\n5. 插入雞脾最厚個位睇下有冇流血水, 如冇流血水, 係流清水, 姐係雞脾應該熟左. 完成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 雞脾浸煮時間事符雞脾大細而定, 不能一慨而論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243b8350fd3d4f8d3a1b37e2e007406c3efd3cce","tid":465044,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:06:21.000Z","msg":"咁多步驟煮咁耐<br />\n<br />\n食兩啖就無<br />\n<br />\n不如出街食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512097166be745f64f00a471c6de22cde562237a","tid":465044,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:10:29.000Z","msg":"幾時整炸脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d4d8a7d914160e845da6531991e62fe2f1016a","tid":465044,"uid":59100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:12:02.000Z","msg":"終於開返煮食post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031f253de90885cc8c86df13197836fcfd4bdc0b","tid":465044,"uid":74981,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多步驟煮咁耐<br />\n<br />\n食兩啖就無<br />\n<br />\n不如出街食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過自己整個味正d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813fdb98a32254c32fd6fac269a7da4f488fcb9e","tid":465044,"uid":74981,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時整炸脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要好大獲油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6605a27275057b64f2c45cabc9a4848d6173cef2","tid":465044,"uid":74981,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:15:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於開返煮食post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI am back<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab94a2f760dca8632d1a8e7cbe3eff6865ad4d4","tid":465044,"uid":62856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:16:48.000Z