 />\n但真係太多功夫，落街買食完瞓醒都未整好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5871573201d5d4c40dbc658fdb776e922861d928","tid":465044,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個色好靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e621eff224dbd13b79dd7916ba6a49320e7d0ce","tid":465044,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鹵髀好正呀狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真係太多功夫，落街買食完瞓醒都未整好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吉妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係呀，所以好少整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db3943cf905bf98937bf03b0a467701a8b4ca4a","tid":465044,"uid":72872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"皮光肉滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ecea4383f872f95eb91e2eabba98d4fc2d192a0","tid":465044,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:21:10.000Z","msg":"本黎好奇怪點解個post高汁左<br />\n原來我block柒左隻肥西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2db76403fdf6751e0a44095e06db4444e7ef48f","tid":465044,"uid":40771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T22:35:45.000Z","msg":"小二 我要兩隻外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70aad1a51adf3f5222f7f28e8360c9ea2d6c7f14","tid":465044,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T02:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皮光肉滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blo